trans-unit.source: Provides methods and properties for all activity designers that display parallel vertical layouts on a workflow design surface.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder egenskaper og metoder for alle aktiviteten utviklere som viser parallelle loddrett oppsett på en arbeidsflyt utformingsoverflaten.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] An activity designer that displays a parallel vertical layout represents an activity on the workflow design surface that has two code paths that a workflow can follow.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]En Aktivitetsdesigner som viser et parallelle loddrett oppsett representerer en aktivitet på arbeidsflyt utformingsoverflaten som har to kodebaner som en arbeidsflyt kan følge.

trans-unit.source: For example, the designer used for the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IfElseActivity> activity displays the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IfElseActivity> activity on the workflow design surface and has a parallel vertical layout.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel designer brukes for den <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IfElseActivity>aktiviteten viser den <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IfElseActivity>aktivitet på arbeidsflyten utforme overflate og har en parallell loddrett oppsett.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IfElseActivity> </xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IfElseActivity>

trans-unit.source: Each branch of the parallel layout visually represents an <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IfElseBranchActivity> activity contained in the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IfElseActivity> activity.
trans-unit.target: Hver gren for parallelle oppsettet visuelt representerer en <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IfElseBranchActivity>aktiviteten i den <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IfElseActivity>aktiviteten.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IfElseActivity> </xref:System.Workflow.Activities.IfElseBranchActivity>

trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.HitTestInfo"> </xref> som beskriver plasseringen til å flytte aktiviteter i.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> read-only collection that contains the activities to move.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> skrivebeskyttet samling som inneholder aktivitetene å flytte.

trans-unit.source: Gets the first selectable object in the navigation order of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter den første valgbar objektet i navigasjon rekkefølgen på den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: If the designer's <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner.Expanded%2A> property or the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner.IsVisible%2A> property is set to `false`, FirstSelectableObject returns a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Hvis utformeren <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner.Expanded%2A>egenskapen eller <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner.IsVisible%2A>er satt til `false`, FirstSelectableObject returnerer en nullreferanse (`Nothing` i Visual Basic).</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner.IsVisible%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner.Expanded%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner.ContainedDesigners%2A> property count is greater than 0, FirstSelectableObject returns the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> associated with the first activity designer in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner.ContainedDesigners%2A>egenskapen antallet er større enn 0, returnerer FirstSelectableObject den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>knyttet til den første aktivitet designeren i samlingen.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner.ContainedDesigners%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets the last selectable object in the navigation order of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter den siste valgbar objekt i navigasjon rekkefølgen på den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: If the designer's <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner.Expanded%2A> or <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner.IsVisible%2A> property is set to `false`, LastSelectableObject returns a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner> contains child activity designers, LastSelectableObject returns the last selectable object associated with the first child activity designer.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner>inneholder underordnede aktiviteten utviklere, LastSelectableObject Returnerer siste valgbar objekt som er tilknyttet den første underordnede aktiviteten designeren.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner>

trans-unit.source: If the child activity designer is collapsed, LastSelectableObject returns the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> associated with the first activity designer in the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner.ContainedDesigners%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: Hvis underordnede Aktivitetsdesigner er skjult, LastSelectableObject returnerer den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>knyttet til den første aktiviteten designeren i den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner.ContainedDesigners%2A>samlingen.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner.ContainedDesigners%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>

trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Object>som siste valgbar objekt i rekkefølgen som designer navigasjon.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Indicates that the user has created a new branch activity on the activity associated with the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Angir at brukeren har opprettet en ny gren aktivitet på aktiviteten tilknyttet den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner"> </xref>.

trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity"> </xref> som ble lagt til som den nye grenen for aktiviteten tilknyttet den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner"> </xref>.

trans-unit.target: Utfører oppsettet oppgaver for å plassere visuelle indikatorer og underordnede utviklere på den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner"> </xref>.

trans-unit.target: einneholder en nullreferanse ( i Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of designer verbs to be associated with the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter samlingen av designer verbene som er knyttet til den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The Verbs property determines the commands that are displayed on the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner> context menu.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen verb bestemmer kommandoer som vises på den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner>hurtigmenyen.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner>

trans-unit.source: The verb collection includes any designer verbs <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner> inherits from the designer classes it extends.
trans-unit.target: Verb-samlingen inneholder Spørringsutformer verb <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner>arver fra designer klassene den utvider.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerVerbCollection"></xref> that contains the designer verbs to associate with the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerVerbCollection"> </xref> som inneholder designer verb som skal knyttes til det <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ParallelActivityDesigner"> </xref>.
